<i>adjective</i>: 넉살좋다 [넉쌀조타], 넉살스럽다 [넉쌀스럽따], 넉살맞다 [넉쌀맏따] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>넉살좋다 [넉쌀조타]</dt><br>
<dd>unblushing; bold-faced</dd><br>
<dd>쑥스러움이 없이 남과 잘 사귀며 비위가 좋다.</dd><br>
<dd>Cheeky and sociable without being too self-conscious.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>넉살스럽다 [넉쌀스럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>unblushing; bold-faced</dd><br>
<dd>쑥스러움이 없이 비위가 좋고 질긴 데가 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Cheeky and tenacious without being too self-conscious.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>넉살맞다 [넉쌀맏따]</dt><br>
<dd>unblushing; bold-faced</dd><br>
<dd>쑥스러움이 없이 매우 비위가 좋다.</dd><br>
<dd>Very daring without being too self-conscious.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>